  <brief_title>A Study of MDX-1106 to Treat Patients With Hepatitis C Infection</brief_title>
  <acronym>MDX1106-02</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase I, Double-blind,Multicenter,Randomized,Placebo-controlled,Safety and Pharmacokinetic Dose-escalation Study of a Single Intravenous Administration of MDX-1106, a Fully Human Monoclonal Antibody to PD-1, in Subjects With Active Hepatitis C Genotype 1 Infection</official_title>
