  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study examines the safety, tolerability, and immunogenicity of a single dose of MDX-1106
      in patients with active hepatitis C genotype 1 or mixed hepatitis C genotype infection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
